  "name": "Breath Weapon",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/creatures/abilities/dragon-ice-breath-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Your breath becomes a Natural Weapon called your Breath Weapon. You can use your Breath Weapon to make a Ranged or Area Martial Attack. Before making the Attack, you can spend 1 or more AP, SP, MP, or a combination of each to increase the damage.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Ranged Attack:</strong> You spend 1 AP to make a Ranged Martial Attack against 1 target’s PD within 10 Spaces.</p><p><strong>Hit:</strong> The target takes 1 Draconic damage (+1 per additional AP or SP spent or +2 per MP spent).</p></li><li><p><strong>Area Attack:</strong> You spend 2 AP to make an Area Martial Attack against every target’s AD within a 2 Space Cone or 4 Space Line.</p><p><strong>Hit:</strong> The target takes 1 Draconic damage (+1 per additional 2 AP, 2 SP, or 1 MP spent).</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Mana and Stamina usage is not automated, you need to keep track of that yourself.</em></p>",
